Lightning C Tool Library Extensions to ISO Standards
----------------------------------------------------

- octal and hexadecimal floating-point constants are supported.
- __CC_ALIGN__(alignment) aligns objects to a given boundary.
- __CC_CACHE_ALIGN__ aligns objects to cache-line boundary.
- __CC_PAGE_ALIGN__ aligns objects to page boundary.

Here's an example of how to align objects in memory:

struct foo bar __CC_PAGE_ALIGN__;

